701488f-a.title: Bronx: Morris Park Avenue - Matthews Avenue
701488f-a.text:
Morris Park Avenue, adjoining, and east of the S. E.
oorner of Matthews Avenue. The first house is number 832.
June 22, 1940
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIO11

701489f-a.title: Bronx: Morris Park Avenue - Matthews Avenue
701489f-a.text:
Morris Park Avenue, at, and adjoining the N. W. corner
of Matthews Avenue. An old street, named Rose Street, once
passed hard by the wall of the 1-story frame taxpayer.
June 22, 1940
P. L. Sperr

701490f-a.title: Bronx: Morris Park Avenue - Matthews Avenue
701490f-a.text:
Morris Park Avenue, north side, east from Matthews
Avenue to Delancey Place. Iw the foreground, near Mullins
Avenue, is the Bronx Free Church.
June 22, 1940
P. L. Sperr
